    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697860/extras/steam_description_01.gif?t=1751345616\" /></span><br><br>《倾听画语》就像是一本生动的小说、一部可互动的电影，讲述一位追逐梦想的画家，为了完成心目中的完美作品，不曾停下她的画笔。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697860/extras/steam_description_02.gif?t=1751345616\" /></span><br><br>你将扮演一名追逐梦想的画家，找寻那些使你的画作鲜活却已遗失的色彩。只有在偶尔休息片刻时，来杯咖啡和早餐让你提振精神继续创作。藉由创作的每一幅绘画作品，感受其中述说的故事。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697860/extras/steam_description_03.gif?t=1751345616\" /></span><br><br>透过点击与拖曳，你能以随心所欲的步调尽情享受轻鬆、扣人心弦的游戏体验。并在流畅悠扬的配乐下，沉浸于充满绚烂色彩与精緻逐格动画的全景世界。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697860/extras/steam_description_04.gif?t=1751345616\" /></span>",
